CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 10, 1946, pg. 20, reads: "Family Reunion - Mrs. Georgia Herbert and daughter, Vera Mathews, of San Pedro, Calif., met Mr. and Mrs. Stanley Herbert from Caledonia, N. Y., during a family reunion held here recently. The above photo was taken at a gay celebration and includes several of the Herbert relatives. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five women, including Georgia Herbert, Vera Mathews, and Mrs. Herbert;  five men including Stanley Herbert, and three girls, gathered on and around sofa in domestic interior with portrait on wall on right
